data.name: Gravekeeper's Watcher
data.desc: During either player's turn, when your opponent activates a Spell/Trap Card or monster effect that could make them discard when it resolves: You can send this card from your hand to the Graveyard; negate the activation, and if you do, destroy it.

card_sets.set_name: Legendary Collection 3: Yugi's World Mega Pack
